node_modules/
# The catalog payload (spool .tgz + per-harness entry.json) IS committed — it's the in-repo
# distribution that a bump PR carries and that `weft` installs from. Only the incremental
# build-state stays local (it's machine/cache-specific, not part of the catalog).
spools/.build-state.json
# Stray npm-pack tarballs from capture, but NOT the committed spool archives.
*.tgz
!spools/**/*.spool.tgz
# Regenerated each run; surfaced as a workflow artifact / issue / PR body.
livecheck-report.md
pr-body.md
.DS_Store
